Class ByteArrayJFO

java.lang.Object
  javax.tools.SimpleJavaFileObject
      es.ull.isaatc.simulation.factory.ByteArrayJFO
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.tools.FileObject, javax.tools.JavaFileObject
public class ByteArrayJFO
extends javax.tools.SimpleJavaFileObject

Creates a Java file object which accepts byte codes on its input stream, and sends them to its output stream. It also allows the output stream to be accessed as a byte array.

ycallero
